          </p><p id="S5LV0669P0-04914"><sup>*</sup> Depreciation, which forms part of resource DEL, is excluded from the total DEL, in the table above. since capital DEL includes capital spending and to include depreciation of those assets would lead to double counting.</p><p id="S5LV0669P0-04915">Within the administration cost limits changes, the impact is set out in the following table:
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">DfES</span></td>
